paragraph.paragraph:
The Other Project Items folder (
	../../../../images/icons/folder.ico
) is the fourth top-level folder of an EiffelEnvision project.xmlProject. Like all other top-level folders, Other Project Items cannot be removed from a project.

Other Project Files only allows New Folders and Existing Items to be added to it, or any of it's sub-folders (
	../../../../images/icons/folder.ico
). To learn how to add new folders or existing items, see the respective urlAdding New Folders and/or urlAdding Existing Items documentation.
